page.title: ServerlessDays ANZ - Alicia Cheah
page.description: Alicia is a senior content leader with over a decade of experience commissioning and developing high quality multimedia content to drive business goals. Alicia is passionate about education and has worked for companies such as Oxford University Press, A Cloud Guru, and Pluralsight. /n/n She also has events management, brand and social media marketing experience and loves creating community experiences to bring people together. /n/n Alicia is a fan of horror movies, needle crafts, and video games.
